en-37e8afd6-496b-4761-a610-4c3bcbf28d89, rgb(255, 255, 255)); --framer-link-text-color: rgb(0, 153, 255); --framer-link-text-decoration: underline; transform: none; opacity: 1;\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-pk5f8l\" data-styles-preset=\"Epu0NqScc\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, var(--token-37e8afd6-496b-4761-a610-4c3bcbf28d89, rgb(255, 255, 255)))\">Contact</p></div></div></a><!--/$--></div><div class=\"framer-8yv902-container\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-Uwt48 framer-7x1yD framer-63yo3f framer-v-aa1myy framer-1pe5h04\" data-framer-name=\"Secondary\" data-highlight=\"true\" style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%; opacity: 1;\" href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/verve-ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"framer-t3x1up\" data-framer-name=\"Container\" style=\"--12gp6ac: 8px 12px 8px 12px; background-color: rgb(0, 201, 167); border-radius: 100px; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-17gd20u\" style=\"--extracted-r6o4lv: rgb(255, 255, 255); --framer-link-text-color: rgb(0, 153, 255); --framer-link-text-decoration: underline; transform: none; opacity: 1;\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-pk5f8l\" data-styles-preset=\"Epu0NqScc\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, rgb(255, 255, 255))\">Shopify App</p></div></div></a><!--/$--></div><div class=\"framer-rkpwjr-container\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-Uwt48 framer-7x1yD framer-63yo3f framer-v-16d026t framer-1pe5h04\" data-framer-name=\"Purple\" data-highlight=\"true\" style=\"height: 100%; opacity: 1;\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/verve-ai-inventory-forecasting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"framer-t3x1up\" data-framer-name=\"Container\" style=\"--12gp6ac: 8px 12px 8px 12px; background-color: rgb(128, 72, 245); border-radius: 100px; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-17gd20u\" style=\"--extracted-r6o4lv: rgb(255, 255, 255); --framer-link-text-color: rgb(0, 153, 255); --framer-link-text-decoration: underline; transform: none; opacity: 1;\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-pk5f8l\" data-styles-preset=\"Epu0NqScc\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, rgb(255, 255, 255))\">WooCommerce App</p></div></div></a><!--/$--></div></div></div></header></div></div></div></div><style data-framer-html-style=\"\">html body { background: rgb(245, 245, 245); }</style><div data-framer-root=\"\" class=\"framer-D5j28 framer-dNysf framer-1jKPC framer-LWPyD framer-gUzfC framer-1wigiej\" style=\"min-height:100vh;width:auto;display:contents\"><div class=\"framer-10v3qp2\"><div class=\"framer-zk5af\" style=\"transform:none\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><h1 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-hqv2qo\" data-styles-preset=\"kx7Q6WsHD\">Free Tools for E-Commerce &amp; Shopify Merchants</h1><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Running an e-commerce business is hard enough without getting buried in spreadsheets. That’s why we’re building a growing collection of free, operator-friendly tools designed to help you understand your numbers, make smarter decisions, and run a healthier, more profitable business.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">These tools are fast, accurate, and purpose-built for founders, operators, and inventory managers who want clarity—not complexity.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Whether you’re forecasting demand, analysing inventory, improving margins, or planning purchasing, these resources give you the insights you need in just a few clicks.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">What You’ll Find Here</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Our library includes easy-to-use calculators, templates, and scorecards covering the most important e-commerce fundamentals:</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Inventory management tools</p><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"./tools/inventory-days-calculator\">Inventory Days Calculator</a><!--/$--></p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"./tools/reorder-point-calculator\">Reorder Point Calculator</a><!--/$--></p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"./tools/inventory-control-excel\">Inventory Control Excel File</a><!--/$--></p></li></ul><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Financial &amp; margin tools</p><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"./tools/ecommerce-profit-margin-calculator\">E-Commerce Profit Margin Calculator</a><!--/$--></p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"./tools/sales-forecast-template\">Sales Forecast Template</a><!--/$--></p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"./tools/cashflow-forecast-template\">Cashflow Forecast Template</a><!--/$--></p></li></ul><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Each tool is available as a free Google Sheet and many can be embedded directly into your workflow.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Why These Tools Exist</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">These tools are built from real challenges we’ve faced working with e-commerce brands:</p><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Overstock tying up cash</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Stockouts killing growth</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Guesswork in purchasing</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Margin erosion</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Endless spreadsheets</p></li></ul><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">We built these resources to make complex calculations simple—and to help operators take control of their numbers.</p><h2 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1b3gxfz\" data-styles-preset=\"nBYoYjZot\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">Built by Verve AI</strong></h2><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">These micro-tools are part of the wider Verve AI ecosystem:<br class=\"framer-text\">an AI-powered demand forecasting and purchasing engine built specifically for Shopify merchants.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">If you want to move beyond spreadsheets and automate forecasting, purchasing, and inventory planning, Verve AI gives you the full system behind the tools.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/verve-ai?utm_source=blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">👉 <strong class=\"framer-text\">View Verve AI on the Shopify App Store</strong></a><!--/$--></p></div></div></div><div id=\"overlay\"></div><div class=\"framer-1h2kvss\"></div><div class=\"framer-lsv2fh\" data-framer-name=\"Footer\"><div class=\"ssr-variant hidden-v3h10d hidden-907ff8\"><div class=\"framer-ihe3tg-container\"><footer class=\"framer-qm2kR framer-98yyr framer-oXIyl framer-zKijR framer-LWPyD framer-qm5p50 framer-v-qm5p50\" data-framer-name=\"Desktop\" style=\"background-color: rgb(19, 33, 68); width: 100%; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-15ufsj5\" data-framer-name=\"Inner\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-6ttnxu\" data-framer-name=\"List\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-1ofpdd9\" data-framer-name=\"Title\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-8wi8wv-container\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-uL3sp framer-1i9bryg framer-v-1i9bryg framer-1hend0p\" data-framer-name=\"Default\" style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%; opacity: 1;\" href=\"./\"><div class=\"framer-4f2q0f\" data-framer-name=\"Logo\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0\" data-framer-background-image-wrapper=\"true\"><img decoding=\"auto\" width=\"940\" height=\"469\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 150px, (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1199.98px) 367px, (max-width: 809.98px) 150px\" srcset=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/zplhvSQDvA45ptNBhwmtoWBGiU0.png?scale-down-to=512 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/zplhvSQDvA45ptNBhwmtoWBGiU0.png 940w\" src=\"https://framerus