  "bodyText": "Home\n\nAbout\n\nContact\n\nShopify App\n\nWooCommerce App\n\nFree Tools for E-Commerce & Shopify Merchants\n\nRunning an e-commerce business is hard enough without getting buried in spreadsheets. That’s why we’re building a growing collection of free, operator-friendly tools designed to help you understand your numbers, make smarter decisions, and run a healthier, more profitable business.\n\nThese tools are fast, accurate, and purpose-built for founders, operators, and inventory managers who want clarity—not complexity.\n\nWhether you’re forecasting demand, analysing inventory, improving margins, or planning purchasing, these resources give you the insights you need in just a few clicks.\n\nWhat You’ll Find Here\n\nOur library includes easy-to-use calculators, templates, and scorecards covering the most important e-commerce fundamentals:\n\nInventory management tools\n\nInventory Days Calculator\n\nReorder Point Calculator\n\nInventory Control Excel File\n\nFinancial & margin tools\n\nE-Commerce Profit Margin Calculator\n\nSales Forecast Template\n\nCashflow Forecast Template\n\nEach tool is available as a free Google Sheet and many can be embedded directly into your workflow.\n\nWhy These Tools Exist\n\nThese tools are built from real challenges we’ve faced working with e-commerce brands:\n\nOverstock tying up cash\n\nStockouts killing growth\n\nGuesswork in purchasing\n\nMargin erosion\n\nEndless spreadsheets\n\nWe built these resources to make complex calculations simple—and to help operators take control of their numbers.\n\nBuilt by Verve AI\n\nThese micro-tools are part of the wider Verve AI ecosystem:\nan AI-powered demand forecasting and purchasing engine built specifically for Shopify merchants.\n\nIf you want to move beyond spreadsheets and automate forecasting, purchasing, and inventory planning, Verve AI gives you the full system behind the tools.\n\n👉 View Verve AI on the Shopify App Store\n\nAI Forecasting Software for E-Commerce Businesses\n\nQuick Links\n\nHome\n\nAbout\n\nPricing\n\nWhy Verve AI\n\nContact\n\nBlog\n\nTools\n\nImportant\n\nVerve AI Shopify\n\nVerve AI WooCommerce\n\nTwitter\n\nPrivacy Policy\n\nTerms\n\nFAQ\n\nGet in Touch\n\nHello@GetVerveAI.com\n\nCopyright © 2026 Verve AI. All rights reserved.",
